data.description: Welcome to 5304 Wentworth Court. This 4 bedroom 2 bath home is just waiting for its new owners to call it home. Once you enter the front door, you are greeted by the spacious family room adjacent to the kitchen with custom bench seating, and eat in breakfast bar, both overlooking the spacious backyard. This one is an entertainers dream. This home features a split bedroom floorplan for everyone to have their own space and  privacy. This home has lots of storage with newly added storage shed and two car garage. Location is right in the heart of Mobile, close to local swim and racquet club, restaurants and shopping on a quiet cul-de-sac street just 2 blocks from Dodge Elementary school. You really need to see this beauty before it is gone.
